ActBankruptcy and Insolvency Act
SubjectRules Amending the Bankruptcy and Insolvency General Rules (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRules Amending the BANKRUPTCY AND INSOLVENCY GENERAL RULES (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) to correct technical errors introduced during the printing of the Rules Amending the Bankruptcy and Insolvency General Rules in March 2007. These amendments will restore those portions of the text that were inadvertently omitted and ensure that both the French and English versions correspond.
